ÉQA^<?php exit; ?>a:1:{s:7:"content";O:8:"stdClass":24:{s:2:"ID";i:658;s:11:"post_author";s:2:"11";s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2017-06-27 06:45:25";s:13:"post_date_gmt";s:19:"2017-06-27 06:45:25";s:12:"post_content";s:7942:"[vc_row][vc_column][woodmart_title font_weight="700" align="left" title="WISAKI FAQs" woodmart_css_id="5d36ee2ce4658" title_width="100"][vc_tta_accordion shape="square" color="white" c_icon="chevron" c_position="right" active_section="1" no_fill="true" collapsible_all="true"][vc_tta_section title="What is Wisaki?" tab_id="1484652030151-41d816a1-ec06"][vc_column_text text_larger="no"]Wisaki is an online marketplace that gives you a wide variety of unique items which
can be shopped from the comfort of your house, office or even on transit. It is also a platform where you can sell your commodities to a diverse market. Items bought are delivered at your doorstep.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="How do I register on Wisaki?" tab_id="1484652030190-407b08ef-5de7"][vc_column_text text_larger="no"]
<ul>
 	<li>To register as a user, please visit www.wisaki.co.ke ( Use Google Chrome and Mozilla Firefox browsers for the best experience)</li>
 	<li>Click on "Register" on the top right corner of Wisaki website.</li>
 	<li>Provide your name and contact number, create a username with your email address and a password. You will be requested to confirm password.</li>
 	<li>Then Create account.</li>
</ul>
[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Do I have to create a new account if I already have an existing account?" tab_id="1484652030219-c6960c7e-ee62"][vc_column_text text_larger="no"]No, you don't. You can however edit your account information such as your `Shipping' and `Billing' addresses, update your email address and password by following the steps below:
<ul>
 	<li>Log in to your account</li>
 	<li>Click `My Account' and then select 'Account Information'</li>
</ul>
[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="What do I do in case I have forgotten my password?" tab_id="1484652030238-302a2c7c-fe6f"][vc_column_text text_larger="no"]Please visit the login page and click on the link next to `Forgot your password?'; enter the details of the email address that you used when you first registered your account.
We will email you a link to this email address which you can click on to reset your password.
If you are still unsuccessful in resetting your password, you may contact the Wisaki Customer Support Team through email on help@wisaki.co.ke or chat.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Can I change my account information?" tab_id="1484652030262-e10da133-51b0"][vc_column_text text_larger="no"]Yes, you can.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Can I pay on delivery?" tab_id="1563881378650-13840f49-6dbb"][vc_column_text text_larger="no"]Yes[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="What is the cost of delivery?" tab_id="1563881412162-6281403a-0504"][vc_column_text text_larger="no"]Our delivery services are based on three key factors; service type, weight, and destination. The cost will however be displayed when placing the order.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="What is Wisaki's Return and Refund policy?" tab_id="1563881501003-8516591e-1474"][vc_column_text text_larger="no"]Please find all the details on the return and refunds policies <a href="https://wisaki.co.ke/return-policy/">here</a>. You can contact us on our various channels listed in the segment below should you need any clarification.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="How can I contact Wisaki in case I have any issues?" tab_id="1563881587251-01f24d67-14fc"][vc_column_text text_larger="no"]You can contact us on;
‚Ä¢ Chat Widget: By logging on to the website and clicking on the chat icon
‚Ä¢ Email: info@wisaki.co.ke
‚Ä¢ Twitter: WisakiKenya
‚Ä¢ Facebook: WisakiKenya[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="How soon from the time of ordering will my item be delivered?" tab_id="1563881649857-df45d759-400f"][vc_column_text text_larger="no"]Your package will be available within 1 business day for Express Orders and 3 business days for Standard delivery. ( Visit <a href="https://wisaki.co.ke/shipping-and-delivery-policy/">Shipping and Delivery Policy</a> for more details)[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Can I cancel my delivery after I place the order?" tab_id="1563881742512-2af6f434-a1b3"][vc_column_text text_larger="no"]We allow for cancellation of the order at any point before it is shipped. Once it is shipped, you can reject it (without opening the package) once delivered, to go back with the rider. Please note that the refund will be exclusive of shipping fees.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="What happens if a product I ordered is out of stock?" tab_id="1563881795013-49ac74dc-c8e5"][vc_column_text text_larger="no"]Being a market place, sometimes, our sellers sell out very quickly on their stock. We put in our best effort to ensure that this does not happen. We commit to notifying you as soon as it happens and offer store credits or refunds in case there are no alternatives[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="If I'm not at home can the delivery be left with a neighbour or with the security office/guard?" tab_id="1563881830397-aa41b230-29fe"][vc_column_text text_larger="no"]Yes, you can. Please ensure that you notify us on email or chat with the name and ID of the person collecting. Please advise the designated person to review the condition of the products order. Kindly review the terms and conditions of returns to get further information.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="When can I place my order?" tab_id="1563881865540-13bfff20-eadd"][vc_column_text text_larger="no"]You can place your order at any time. Deliveries however will be done as per the timelines noted on the check-out page.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="How do I place an order on Wisaki?" tab_id="1563881901184-a1e79df4-e535"][vc_column_text text_larger="no"]Once you log on to wisaki.co.ke, you can search for items by;
<ul>
 	<li>Searching for the products by keying the product on the 'Search' bar</li>
 	<li>Browsing the 'Category menu'</li>
 	<li>Contacting Masoko Support Agents through the chat and request for the product(s) if you have a challenge in navigation</li>
 	<li>Once you find the items, click the "Add to Cart" button.After adding the item to the cart, a popup on the side will appear, giving you the options to either continue shopping or to check out. You can also click on 'My</li>
 	<li>Cart' to check out.</li>
 	<li>If you have an account and have not logged on, you will be prompted to 'Sign In' to your account or if you do not have an account, you will be required to 'Register' and create a new account if this is your first order.</li>
 	<li>You can also check out as a guest.</li>
 	<li>Enter a 'Shipping Address, choose a shipping method, and enter your payment information.</li>
 	<li>Review your order details. Be sure you've applied any Gift Cards or promotional codes you would like to use on your order.</li>
 	<li>Click 'Place your order'.</li>
 	<li>Once payment has gone through you will then receive an email with the order details, and a text that the order has been confirmed.</li>
</ul>
[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="What options do I have to make a Payment?" tab_id="1563882027755-4e87220f-194d"][vc_column_text text_larger="no"]
<ul>
 	<li>M-PESA, Visa, Master Card.</li>
 	<li>Pay On Delivery</li>
</ul>
[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="How secure is our payment platform?" tab_id="1563882066403-ff9bbea5-77e0"][vc_column_text text_larger="no"]We take with utmost caution to satisfy our customers trust in their information and money. Our payment service provider is PCI DSS level 1 compliant, and our payment pages use SSL with 256-bit encryption)[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][/vc_tta_accordion][/vc_column][/vc_row]";s:10:"post_title";s:4:"FAQs";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:0:"";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:6:"closed";s:11:"ping_status";s:6:"closed";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:4:"faqs";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2019-10-24 11:07:09";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2019-10-24 08:07:09";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";i:0;s:4:"guid";s:51:"http://dummy.xtemos.com/woodmart/demos/?page_id=658";s:10:"menu_order";i:0;s:9:"post_type";s:4:"page";s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"0";s:6:"filter";s:3:"raw";}}